To run this code you need to install all the given dependencies in the exact same folder as the project
 - MongoDB
 - Mongod
 - Express
 - body-parser
 - nodemon
 
Then open the terminal in the project folder, type
"nodemon index.js"
then press enter. This will run the server on port 5500.

Now go to your browser and open your localhost
"http://localhost:5500" and your website will be visible
